Smt-Segmentation (formerly known as Educe, not to be confused with https://github.com/viscenter/educe) is part of the Scroll Manipulation Toolkit.

The program needs JOGL to interface in between Java and OpenGL. It can be downloaded here: https://jogamp.org/deployment/jogamp-current/archive/jogamp-all-platforms.7z

The necessary .jar files can be copied from these extracted files to somewhere Java can find them (on OS X: /Library/Java/Extensions/). The following files are needed on OS X:

gluegen-rt-natives-macosx-universal.jar
gluegen-rt.jar
jogl-all-natives-macosx-universal.jar
jogl-all.jar

The naming changes for other platforms are self explanatory.